content_html: National Assembly Chairman Narayan Prasad Dahal met with the newly appointed Prime Minister, Sushila Karki, to offer his congratulations and best wishes for a successful term. The meeting took place on Tuesday morning at the Prime Minister's official residence in Baluwatar.
